Available Tools: set_volume | get_volume | mute | unmute | set_equalizer
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "level": number, "preset": "string" }
Response Schema: { "volume": number, "muted": boolean, "equalizer_preset": "string" }
---
Question: Adjust the sound profile to electronic for the dance party.
Call: { "func_call": "set_equalizer", "level": 0, "preset": "electronic" }
Response: { "volume": 82, "muted": false, "equalizer_preset": "electronic" }

